## 🛠️ Regra Customizada (Exemplo)

```xml
<rule id="100500" level="12">
  <if_group>sysmon_event1</if_group>
  <field name="win.eventdata.image">powershell.exe</field>
  <field name="win.eventdata.commandLine">-enc|-nop|-w hidden</field>
